Edwin H. Shuford III
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President and Chief Credit Officer at YADKIN FINANCIAL CORP, Edwin H. Shuford III made $958,377 in total compensation.  Of this total $275,000 was received as a salary, $295,000 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $346,800 was awarded as stock and $41,577 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


